ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How often is the transaction data updated?

FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common queries about our Ethereum transaction finder app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What is this Ethereum transaction finder app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app is a powerful tool designed to help you discover and track new Ethereum transactions in real-time. It provides an easy-to-use interface for monitoring the Ethereum blockchain and staying up-to-date with the latest transaction activities.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: The app connects to the Ethereum blockchain and continuously scans for new transactions. It then presents this information in a user-friendly format, allowing you to filter, sort, and analyze transactions based on various criteria such as address, value, or smart contract interactions.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I set up alerts for specific types of transactions?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Yes, you can customize alerts based on your preferences. Set up notifications for transactions involving specific addresses, exceeding certain ETH values, or interacting with particular smart contracts. Stay informed about the transactions that matter most to you.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is this app suitable for both beginners and experienced Ethereum users?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Absolutely! Our app is designed with an intuitive interface that caters to users of all experience levels. Beginners can easily track basic transaction details, while advanced users can access more complex features for in-depth analysis and monitoring.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How frequently is the transaction data updated?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Our app updates transaction data in near real-time, typically within seconds of a transaction being added to the Ethereum blockchain. This ensures you have the most up-to-date information at your fingertips for timely decision-making and analysis.
